The '''Holitsynske gas field''' [[natural gas field]] located on the continental shelf of the [[Black Sea]]. It was discovered in 1974 and developed by [[Chornomornaftogaz]]. It started commercial production in 1975. The total [[proven reserves]] of the Holitsynske gas field are around {{convert|544|e9cuft}}, and production is slated to be around {{convert|20|e6cuft/d}} in 2015.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.geoecomar.ro/website/publicatii/Nr.3-1998/3.VasylISozansky.pdf|title=Ukrainian Black Sea gas fields|date=2009|publisher=geoecomar.ro|accessdate=2014-03-27}}</ref>
